    <item>
      <title>乐天股价自 5 月以来最大跌幅，因金融科技重组推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/rakuten-slides-most-since-may-on-fintech-reorganization-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于总部位于东京的在线购物商城运营商乐天集团 (Rakuten Group Inc.) 合并其金融科技业务的计划被推迟，该公司股价一度下跌 6.7%，创下自 5 月份以来的最大盘中跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/rakuten-slides-most-since-may-on-fintech-reorganization-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 02:19:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星开始缩小与 Nvidia 制造 AI 内存芯片的差距</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/samsung-begins-closing-gap-in-making-ai-memory-chips-for-nvidia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司在开发对人工智能市场至关重要的存储芯片方面遭遇一系列挫折后，开始在缩小与竞争对手 SK 海力士公司的差距方面取得进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/samsung-begins-closing-gap-in-making-ai-memory-chips-for-nvidia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 02:15:40 GMT</pubDate>
